snippet.title: Playtonic Friends Presents: BPM: Bullets Per Minute
snippet.description:
Get ready for BPM: Bullets Per Minute coming to the Playstation 4 and Xbox One in 2021!

For more information, check out our news article here: https://bit.ly/32X6NkO 

Follow Playtonic Friends and Awe Interactive on Twitter to be kept up-to-date with more news:
